sentences: Anders Johansson (born 25 May 1962) is a Swedish musician, best known as the former drummer of HammerFall and Yngwie Malmsteen's Rising Force.
From 1979 through 1982 he attended an electronics engineering school.

sentences: In 1984 he moved to the United States to join his brother Jens in Yngwie Malmsteen's band.

sentences: He initially joined HammerFall on the "Legacy" tour in 1999, at first only as a session drummer but later as a full-time member.
